text: Lutz is an unincorporated census-designated place (CDP) in Hillsborough County, Florida, United States. It is fifteen miles north of Tampa. The northern part of Lutz also makes up a portion of south Pasco County. The population was 23,707 at the 2020 census. ==References== Category:Census- designated places in Florida Category:Unincorporated communities in Florida
title: Lutz, Florida
